FBIS4-18114 "drweu062_h_94008" FBIS-WEU-94-062 Daily Report 30 Mar 1994 GERMANY Russian Army Carries Out Unauthorized Explosions Russian Army Carries Out Unauthorized Explosions LD3003205294 Munich ARD Television Network in German 1900 GMT 30 Mar 94 LD3003205294 Munich ARD Television Network German BFN [Text] The Russian military has admitted that it blew up ammunition earlier this month at the military training ground of Colbitz-Letzlinger Heide. The explosions caused earthquake-like tremors and alarmed people living in and around Stendal and Gardelegen. A Russian major general said the withdrawing troops had destroyed ammunition which was old and unsafe to transport. They had neglected to obtain an explosion permit.
